title: I have a Pixel 5 unlocked, using Verizon 5G sim card. But no November update. I checked manually.
content: My unlocked Pixel 5 is not getting the November update.  I have checked manually every few days since it rolled out.  When I had the Verizon Pixel phones, I got the update on the day or came out.  My phone is having many software issues the update looks to fix.
